  <meta itemprop="startDate" content="2016-09-16">
  <meta itemprop="endDate" content="2016-09-17">
  <meta itemprop="url" content="http://becamp.org">
  <meta itemprop="description" content="Open Space Conference">
  <meta itemprop="image" content="<%= image_url 'becamp-large.png' %>">
  Did you know? You can BeTech all year round! Spring = BeSwarm | Fall = BeCamp
